cdata.name: Adamant
cdata.desc: Adamant is a blockchain-based system for data and message transfers that acts alongside an integrated payment system, providing users with a secure and encrypted source for business and personal communications. Adamantfeatures a messenger available for any device, and a corporate system for data and message transfers with an ability to digitally-sign documents and an integrated payment system that allows a company to reduce its internal transactional costs.ADM is a DPoS cryptocurrency used on the platform for secure payments and as an incentive layer.
